pages.title: Jada
pages.text: Jada is a roghe planet that has enter the solar system with it's moon Diater. - (Atmosphere) Jada has decently think atmosphere that has a pink or magent color to and a green sunrise/set! but no oxygen - (Surface) The surface seems to be coverd in a lot of snow and simler to the moon in the none snow areas its surface gravity is about 6.1 m/s.
